# UI Development Focus

This project session is focused on frontend UI work.

- Prioritize visual/interface improvements in `app` (layout, styling, spacing, responsiveness, UX clarity, accessibility, and component presentation).
- Do not change backend/server code, API contracts, database behavior, authentication logic, or business rules unless explicitly requested.
- Avoid introducing logic-heavy refactors when a UI-scoped change solves the request.
- Keep behavior unchanged while improving look-and-feel and interaction polish.
- If a task requires backend changes to complete, pause and ask for explicit approval before proceeding.
